---
layout: base.njk
title: Network View
pageKey: network
permalink: /network/
---

<style>
  /* Help / legend */
  .network-help { margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem; background: #0e0f12; border: 1px solid #2c2c2c; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; }
  .network-help summary { cursor: pointer; padding: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 1rem; }
  .network-help-body { padding-top: 0.5rem; }
  .network-thesis { max-width: 70rem; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; line-height: 1.5; }
  .network-caveats { margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }

  .legend-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .legend-col h4 { margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #aaa; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .legend-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .legend-list li { padding: 0.25rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.4; }

  .lg-shape { display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.4rem; }
  .lg-investor { width: 11px; height: 11px; transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .lg-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .lg-cell { width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 2px; }
  .lg-cell-lp        { background: #c4a83a; }
  .lg-cell-coinvest  { background: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; }
  .lg-cell-coinvest::after { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 50%; width: 6px; height: 6px;
                             background: #c4a83a; border-radius: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
  .lg-cell-both      { background: #c4a83a; position: relative; }
  .lg-cell-both::after { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 50%; width: 4px; height: 4px;
                         background: #0e0f12; border-radius: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
  .lg-dfi        { background: #e25c5c; }
  .lg-vc         { background: #3ed7b3; }
  .lg-foundation { background: #d6b94a; }
  .lg-family     { background: #b86bdf; }
  .lg-government { background: #4a9cd6; }
  .lg-other      { background: #6c8aac; }

  /* View tabs */
  .view-tabs { display: flex; gap: 0; margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #2c2c2c; }
  .view-tab { background: transparent; color: #aaa; border: 1px solid transparent; border-bottom: none;
              padding: 0.5rem 1.1rem; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.9rem;
              text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .view-tab:hover { color: #ddd; }
  .view-tab.active { color: #fa3; border-color: #2c2c2c; border-bottom-color: #0e0f12; background: #0e0f12;
                     position: relative; top: 1px; font-weight: 600; }

  /* Controls */
  .network-controls { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start; padding: 0.5rem 0;
                      flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .ctrl-group { border: 1px solid #2c2c2c; padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem 0.5rem; margin: 0;
                display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.2rem; min-width: 0; }
  .ctrl-group legend { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase;
                       letter-spacing: 0.06em; padding: 0 0.3rem; }
  .ctrl-group label { display: inline-flex; gap: 0.4rem; align-items: center; cursor: pointer;
                      font-size: 0.9rem; white-space: nowrap; }
  .ctrl-group label .lg-shape { flex: 0 0 auto; margin-right: 0; }
  .ctrl-group .ctrl-master { padding-bottom: 0.3rem; border-bottom: 1px dashed #333;
                             margin-bottom: 0.3rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .ctrl-search input { background: #0e0f12; color: #d4d4d4; border: 1px solid #333;
                       padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.9rem; min-width: 14rem; }
  .ctrl-search input:focus { outline: none; border-color: #fa3; }
  .ctrl-radio label { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }

  /* Per-fund picker */
  .ctrl-funds { min-width: 17rem; max-width: 22rem; }
  .ctrl-fund-section { margin-top: 0.4rem; border-top: 1px dashed #2c2c2c; padding-top: 0.3rem; }
  .ctrl-fund-section summary { cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
                               align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.15rem 0; }
  .ctrl-fund-section summary::marker { color: #666; }
  .ctrl-fund-section-title { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #aaa; text-transform: uppercase;
                             letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .ctrl-fund-count { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #888;
                     font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .ctrl-fund-shortcuts { display: flex; gap: 0.3rem; padding: 0.25rem 0 0.4rem; }
  .ctrl-fund-shortcuts button { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
                                background: #1a1a1a; color: #aaa; border: 1px solid #333;
                                cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; }
  .ctrl-fund-shortcuts button:hover { background: #222; color: #d4d4d4; border-color: #555; }
  .ctrl-fund-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.15rem;
                    max-height: 240px; overflow-y: auto; padding-right: 0.4rem; }
  .ctrl-fund-list label { font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.25; padding: 0.1rem 0;
                          white-space: normal; }
  .ctrl-fund-list label.empty-data { opacity: 0.55; }

  /* Selection / details */
  #selection-info { display: block; padding: 0.4rem 0; font-size: 0.85rem; min-height: 1.4em; }
  .network-details { padding: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; background: #0e0f12; border: 1px solid #2c2c2c; }
  .network-details h3 { margin: 0 0 0.3rem 0; }
  .network-details ul { max-height: 260px; overflow-y: auto; padding-left: 1.2rem; }

  /* Visualization wrapper */
  .vis-wrap { position: relative; border: 1px solid #2c2c2c; background: #0e0f12;
              min-height: 600px; overflow: auto; }
  #vis-svg { display: block; }

  /* Matrix-specific */
  .matrix-cell { stroke: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); stroke-width: 0.5px; }
  .matrix-cell-group { transition: opacity 0.12s ease; }
  .matrix-cell-group.dim { opacity: 0.16; }
  .matrix-cell-group.hot .matrix-cell { stroke: #fa3; stroke-width: 1.5px; }
  .matrix-cell-group.hot .matrix-cell-codot { stroke: #fa3; stroke-width: 1px; }
  .matrix-row-label { font-size: 12px; fill: #cfcfcf; text-anchor: end; cursor: pointer;
                      transition: fill 0.12s ease; }
  .matrix-row-label.dim { fill: #555; }
  .matrix-row-label.hot { fill: #fa3; font-weight: 600; }
  .matrix-col-label { font-size: 12px; fill: #cfcfcf; transition: fill 0.12s ease; }
  .matrix-col-label.dim { fill: #555; }
  .matrix-col-label.hot { fill: #fa3; font-weight: 600; }
  .matrix-col-label.non-ingo { font-style: italic; opacity: 0.85; }
  .matrix-row-bg.hot { fill: rgba(255, 170, 51, 0.07); }
  .matrix-row-bg { fill: transparent; }
  .matrix-archetype-dot { stroke: #0e0f12; stroke-width: 1.5px; }
  .matrix-section-divider { stroke: #2c2c2c; stroke-width: 1px; stroke-dasharray: 3 3; }
  .matrix-section-label { font-size: 10px; fill: #888; text-transform: uppercase;
                          letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

  /* Sankey-specific */
  .sankey-node rect { stroke: #0e0f12; stroke-width: 1.5px; cursor: pointer;
                      transition: opacity 0.12s ease; }
  .sankey-node text { font-size: 12px; fill: #cfcfcf; pointer-events: none;
                      transition: fill 0.12s ease; }
  .sankey-node.dim rect { opacity: 0.2; }
  .sankey-node.dim text { fill: #555; }
  .sankey-node.hot rect { stroke: #fa3; stroke-width: 2px; }
  .sankey-node.hot text { fill: #fa3; font-weight: 600; }
  .sankey-link { fill: none; stroke-opacity: 0.4; cursor: pointer;
                 transition: stroke-opacity 0.12s ease; }
  .sankey-link:hover { stroke-opacity: 0.75; }
  .sankey-link.dim { stroke-opacity: 0.08; }
  .sankey-link.hot { stroke-opacity: 0.85; }
  .sankey-col-label { font-size: 11px; fill: #888; text-transform: uppercase;
                      letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-anchor: middle; }
  .sankey-empty-note { fill: #888; font-size: 13px; text-anchor: middle; }

  /* Chord-specific */
  .chord-arc { stroke: #0e0f12; stroke-width: 1.5px; cursor: pointer; }
  .chord-arc.dim { opacity: 0.2; }
  .chord-arc.hot { stroke: #fa3; stroke-width: 2px; }
  .chord-ribbon { fill-opacity: 0.55; stroke-width: 0.5px; cursor: pointer; }
  .chord-ribbon.dim { fill-opacity: 0.05; }
  .chord-ribbon.hot { fill-opacity: 0.85; stroke: #fa3; stroke-width: 1.5px; }
  .chord-label { font-size: 11px; fill: #cfcfcf; cursor: pointer; }
  .chord-label.dim { fill: #555; }
  .chord-label.hot { fill: #fa3; font-weight: 600; }
  .chord-empty-note { fill: #888; font-size: 13px; text-anchor: middle; }

  /* Tooltip */
  #vis-tooltip { position: absolute; pointer-events: none; background: #1a1a1a; color: #d4d4d4;
                 border: 1px solid #444; padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem; font-size: 0.85rem; max-width: 280px;
                 z-index: 20; display: none; line-height: 1.4; }
  #vis-tooltip strong { color: #fa3; }

  /* Loading overlay */
  #vis-loading { position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
                 align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.75rem;
                 background: #0e0f12; color: #aaa; pointer-events: none; z-index: 5; }
  #vis-loading.hidden { display: none; }
  .vis-loading-spinner { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
                         border: 3px solid #2c2c2c; border-top-color: #fa3;
                         animation: vis-spin 0.9s linear infinite; }
  @keyframes vis-spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .vis-loading-spinner { animation: none; } }
</style>

<section class="doc-title">
  <div class="doc-title-tag">
    <span>Investor network · early preview</span>
  </div>
  <h1 class="doc-title-h1">The network of money flowing through INGO impact funds <span class="accent">— who funds whom.</span></h1>
</section>

<section class="sec">

  <details class="network-help">
    <summary><strong>How to read this</strong> <span class="muted">— click to expand</span></summary>
    <div class="network-help-body">

      <p class="network-thesis">
        INGOs raising their first impact-fund close struggle because the visible "impact LPs" are crowded.
        The bigger lead-gen opportunity is <em>generalist investors who already touch impact via co-investments</em>
        — they look like outsiders on a list of impact funders, but they have already deployed capital alongside
        impact funds at the portfolio level. This view maps that network: who funds whom, and where the same
        investor entity shows up in more than one position.
      </p>

      <div class="legend-grid">
        <div class="legend-col">
          <h4>Cell encoding (matrix)</h4>
          <ul class="legend-list">
            <li><span class="lg-shape lg-cell lg-cell-lp"></span> <b>LP</b> — investor put money into the fund</li>
            <li><span class="lg-shape lg-cell lg-cell-coinvest"></span> <b>Co-investor</b> — investor backed a portfolio company of the fund (number = how many)</li>
            <li><span class="lg-shape lg-cell lg-cell-both"></span> <b>Both</b> — LP <em>and</em> co-investor</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="legend-col">
          <h4>Investor archetypes (row dot colour)</h4>
          <ul class="legend-list">
            <li><span class="lg-shape lg-dot lg-dfi"></span> <b>DFI</b> — development finance institution (BII, IFC, US DFC, Norfund …)</li>
            <li><span class="lg-shape lg-dot lg-vc"></span> <b>VC / private fund</b> (Andreessen Horowitz, Coinbase Ventures …)</li>
            <li><span class="lg-shape lg-dot lg-foundation"></span> <b>Foundation</b> (Gates, Skoll …)</li>
            <li><span class="lg-shape lg-dot lg-family"></span> <b>Family office</b> (private wealth)</li>
            <li><span class="lg-shape lg-dot lg-government"></span> <b>Government agency</b> (USAID …)</li>
            <li><span class="lg-shape lg-dot lg-other"></span> <b>Other</b> (donor-advised, mixed, unclassified)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="legend-col">
          <h4>Try this</h4>
          <ul class="legend-list">
            <li>Hover any row or column to highlight its connections.</li>
            <li>Switch to <b>Chord</b> to see funds that share investors with each other.</li>
            <li>Filter by <b>investor type</b> to spotlight VCs, DFIs, foundations …</li>
            <li>Search "BII", "Gates", "Soros" to jump to a specific row.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="muted network-caveats">
        Caveats: portfolio attribution for Kiva is umbrella-level (KRIF is one of several Kiva vehicles).
        Acumen funds are temporarily blocked behind a Cloudflare bot challenge.
        LP coverage is sparse across most funds — it fills in as new fund pages get scraped.
      </p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <div class="view-tabs">
    <button class="view-tab active" data-view="matrix">Matrix · who funds whom</button>
    <button class="view-tab" data-view="chord">Chord · funds that share investors</button>
    <button class="view-tab" data-view="sankey">Bridge · INGO-Backed ↔ Non-INGO-Backed</button>
  </div>

  <div class="network-controls">
